1:35:22.347 --> 1:35:25.309
(rain splattering)

1:35:26.684 --> 1:35:29.478
(beacon humming)

1:35:57.799 --> 1:36:00.219
(tense music)

1:36:03.597 --> 1:36:06.099
(uneasy music)

1:36:23.032 --> 1:36:26.036
(items clattering)

1:36:34.878 --> 1:36:39.216
- I don't like it, Sarge,
it should be right here.

1:36:40.175 --> 1:36:42.094
It must have gone.

1:36:42.094 --> 1:36:45.597
- If it'd gone,
there'd be no signal.

1:36:45.597 --> 1:36:48.559
(rain splattering)

1:36:50.434 --> 1:36:52.896
(tense music)

1:36:58.568 --> 1:37:01.362
(waves crashing)

1:37:04.032 --> 1:37:06.952
(items clattering)

1:37:08.662 --> 1:37:11.123
(tense music)

1:37:20.674 --> 1:37:21.466
- Sarge.

1:37:22.384 --> 1:37:25.137
(waves crashing)

1:37:27.472 --> 1:37:31.059
(rain splattering)

1:37:31.059 --> 1:37:33.520
(tense music)

1:37:41.320 --> 1:37:42.112
- Hello?

1:37:44.740 --> 1:37:45.657
Are you okay?

1:37:53.040 --> 1:37:55.918
(radar beeping)

1:38:01.255 --> 1:38:04.259
(waves crashing)

1:38:09.264 --> 1:38:10.057
Hello.

1:38:12.184 --> 1:38:12.893
Hello?

1:38:13.809 --> 1:38:16.480
(tense music)

1:38:40.587 --> 1:38:41.672
Are you okay?

1:38:48.804 --> 1:38:51.264
(gun booming)

1:38:56.562 --> 1:38:59.356
(uneasy music)

1:39:08.115 --> 1:39:08.907
- Sully.

1:39:11.785 --> 1:39:12.911
I begged him.

1:39:15.664 --> 1:39:18.416
He climbed off
across the plastic

1:39:19.793 --> 1:39:22.045
and he wouldn't come back.

1:39:25.424 --> 1:39:26.216
I'm sorry.

1:39:28.886 --> 1:39:31.889
(Cassidy sobbing)

1:39:39.313 --> 1:39:42.065
(uneasy music)

1:40:01.460 --> 1:40:04.338
(Cassidy gasping)

1:40:12.930 --> 1:40:13.722
Sully?

1:40:56.889 --> 1:41:00.477
(radio squelching)
Sully?

1:41:05.607 --> 1:41:08.693
(radio squelching)
Sully, I'm sorry I slept in.

1:41:08.693 --> 1:41:10.571
Come in, are you there?

1:41:16.493 --> 1:41:18.829
(radio squelching)

1:41:19.162 --> 1:41:20.330
That thing you gave me.

1:41:21.707 --> 1:41:23.416
The metal globe.

1:41:25.377 --> 1:41:27.588
I think I figured
out what it is.

1:41:29.214 --> 1:41:31.258
It's funny, you'll like it.

1:41:31.258 --> 1:41:33.760
(radio squelching)

1:41:33.760 --> 1:41:36.305
(uneasy music)

1:41:39.516 --> 1:41:40.976
(radio squelching)
Sully?

1:41:45.022 --> 1:41:47.691
(door creaking)

1:41:49.735 --> 1:41:50.527
Sully?

1:41:55.365 --> 1:41:56.157
Sullivan?

1:41:58.535 --> 1:42:00.037
(radio squelching)
- I'm here.

1:42:08.003 --> 1:42:10.422
It was his third tour out here.

1:42:10.422 --> 1:42:11.215
Hendrichs.

1:42:13.342 --> 1:42:15.260
He wanted to stay.

1:42:15.260 --> 1:42:16.469
Put that in his report.

1:42:19.348 --> 1:42:20.474
Asking for another shift.

1:42:23.769 --> 1:42:25.062
He didn't want to leave.

1:42:32.027 --> 1:42:33.445
(radio squelching)

1:42:33.445 --> 1:42:37.157
- Sully, his mental state
was so unpredictable.

1:42:40.661 --> 1:42:42.204
You saw what happened to him.

1:42:48.502 --> 1:42:51.588
- [Sullivan] What
did happen to him?

1:42:53.924 --> 1:42:55.759
He didn't kill himself.

1:42:58.094 --> 1:42:59.513
But you know that.

1:43:00.472 --> 1:43:01.264
Don't you?

1:43:08.438 --> 1:43:10.273
And the relief crew?

1:43:11.400 --> 1:43:13.986
(uneasy music)

1:43:18.824 --> 1:43:20.242
I know it was you.

1:43:24.996 --> 1:43:26.832
I know why you're here.

1:43:28.709 --> 1:43:31.295
(uneasy music)

1:43:53.108 --> 1:43:54.860
(radio squelching)
- Sullivan.

1:43:56.320 --> 1:43:59.239
Sullivan, what do you mean?

1:44:00.616 --> 1:44:03.660
I don't understand.
(radio squelching)

1:44:03.660 --> 1:44:06.663
- [Sullivan] I can't
let you have it.

1:44:08.790 --> 1:44:10.501
(radio squelching)

1:44:10.501 --> 1:44:12.252
- Let me have what?

1:44:16.423 --> 1:44:19.425
(bomb whirring)

1:44:23.222 --> 1:44:26.099
(worrisome music)

1:44:26.099 --> 1:44:28.101
(bomb whirring)

1:44:32.814 --> 1:44:35.817
(computer beeping)

1:44:48.246 --> 1:44:51.124
(buttons beeping)

1:44:53.043 --> 1:44:53.835
Sullivan.

1:44:56.713 --> 1:44:58.215
What are you doing?

1:44:58.215 --> 1:45:00.884
I don't understand.
- Just stop.

1:45:03.762 --> 1:45:04.763
- Stop what?

1:45:07.014 --> 1:45:08.016
- It's over.

1:45:10.434 --> 1:45:12.187
You really played me.

1:45:12.187 --> 1:45:12.938
- Sully.

1:45:16.608 --> 1:45:19.443
- Hooked me like
a big dumb fish.

1:45:21.612 --> 1:45:22.364
- No.

1:45:26.702 --> 1:45:28.452
- It never rained on our side.

1:45:30.706 --> 1:45:33.541
(sorrowful music)

1:45:42.718 --> 1:45:44.344
- I hated lying to you (sobs).

1:45:46.889 --> 1:45:50.225
(computer beeping)

1:45:50.225 --> 1:45:53.103
Sully, listen to me.

1:45:53.103 --> 1:45:56.231
- Don't.
- My homeland is sinking.

1:45:56.231 --> 1:45:59.985
My people will perish if I
didn't get hold of that thing.

1:46:01.403 --> 1:46:03.572
All I want is to
end their suffering.

1:46:03.572 --> 1:46:05.365
- So that someone else
would suffer instead?

1:46:07.159 --> 1:46:08.911
No one should have it.

1:46:09.870 --> 1:46:12.496
Not your people, not mine.

1:46:16.210 --> 1:46:17.169
No one.

1:46:17.169 --> 1:46:18.212
(computer beeping)
- Sully.

1:46:18.212 --> 1:46:19.046
- Like you said, Cass.

1:46:20.172 --> 1:46:24.175
We just keep on fucking up.

1:46:26.261 --> 1:46:29.097
(Cassidy sobbing)

1:46:30.724 --> 1:46:32.184
- That's how it is.

1:46:35.312 --> 1:46:37.773
- It doesn't have to be.

1:46:37.773 --> 1:46:42.945
(uplifting music)
(computer beeping)

1:46:45.531 --> 1:46:48.200
(tense music)

1:46:59.378 --> 1:47:02.255
(Cassidy gasping)

1:47:12.349 --> 1:47:15.227
(waves lapping)

1:47:17.521 --> 1:47:20.523
(computer beeping)

1:47:44.715 --> 1:47:45.507
- What?

1:47:49.887 --> 1:47:52.889
(computer beeping)

1:48:00.022 --> 1:48:02.773
(bomb whirring)

1:48:04.193 --> 1:48:05.777
- Baines.

1:48:05.777 --> 1:48:08.780
(bomb whirring)

1:49:10.925 --> 1:49:13.219
We're not leaning anymore.

1:49:15.389 --> 1:49:16.348
- No.

1:49:20.769 --> 1:49:22.521
And we're still here.

1:49:31.737 --> 1:49:32.948
- So what now?

1:49:38.370 --> 1:49:40.205
- Now it's up to us.

1:49:43.541 --> 1:49:45.502
- And if someone comes?

1:49:49.423 --> 1:49:50.215
- Yours?

1:49:53.969 --> 1:49:54.928
- Or yours.

1:49:56.305 --> 1:49:59.099
(tender music)

1:50:00.893 --> 1:50:03.437
- Then we protect the swallows.

1:50:07.858 --> 1:50:08.650
Together.

1:50:14.615 --> 1:50:16.867
And with everything we have.

1:50:27.460 --> 1:50:31.255
- So, what is it?

1:50:32.382 --> 1:50:34.927
(tender music)

1:51:06.291 --> 1:51:08.960
(bird tweeting)

1:51:12.840 --> 1:51:15.634
(birds tweeting)

1:51:18.804 --> 1:51:21.473
(upbeat music)

1:52:21.325 --> 1:52:24.036
(upbeat music)

1:52:53.398 --> 1:52:55.859
